taking a closer look

00:00:25.440 --> 00:00:28.560 align:middle line:84%
at what's going on both
outside and inside,

00:00:28.560 --> 00:00:31.320 align:middle line:84%
so that we can make
empowered choices about what

00:00:31.320 --> 00:00:34.530 align:middle line:84%
