Well, in most parts of the
world, it's getting colder.

00:00:41.280 --> 00:00:43.260 align:middle line:84%
It's also getting
a little bit drier.

00:00:43.260 --> 00:00:46.440 align:middle line:84%
A lot of change is associated
with this time of year, right?

00:00:46.440 --> 00:00:48.930 align:middle line:84%
The autumn into
the early winter.

00:00:48.930 --> 00:00:52.740 align:middle line:84%
And with that change can bring
a little bit of instability

00:00:52.740 --> 00:00:55.287 align:middle line:84%
that can have an impact
on our immune systems.

00:00:55.287 --> 00:00:56.370 align:middle line:90%
And so what are we seeing?

00:00:56.370 --> 00:00:58.320 align:middle line:84%
What's going on with
you this time of year?

00:00:58.320 --> 00:01:00.090 align:middle line:84%
Well, the kinds of
things that I see

00:01:00.090 --> 00:01:03.750 align:middle line:84%
